docs.abstract: The company’s report says streaming subscribers are spending more time in front of a screen.

docs.lead_paragraph: About two in five American households now subscribe to a video streaming service like Netflix, Amazon Prime or Hulu Plus, according to a new report from the media measurement company Nielsen that tracked the penetration of the digital offerings.
